CII Press Release Chatbot
Project Overview
This chatbot helps users ask questions about CII press releases by scraping and processing information from specific CII web pages.

Features
	•	Scrapes press release data (title, summary, date) from CII's website.
	•	Processes user questions to match relevant press releases.
	•	Provides a simple interface built using Streamlit.

Setup Instructions
1. Install Dependencies
Run the following command to install required packages:
pip install requests beautifulsoup4 streamlit nltk


2. Download NLTK Resources
Run this to get NLTK resources for tokenization and stopwords:
import nltk
nltk.download('punkt')
nltk.download('stopwords')

3. Run the App
Use this command to start the Streamlit app:
streamlit run cii_press_release_chatbot.py

How It Works
	1	Scrapes Press Releases: Extracts title, summary, and date from provided URLs.
	2	Processes Questions: Matches user queries with press release summaries using basic word comparison.
	3	Shows Results: Returns relevant press release data based on the question.


